# Short-Form Content Analysis

This repository highlights how I approach short-form video content from an engagement and storytelling perspective.

## Focus Areas

- Hook effectiveness (first 3 seconds)
- Pacing and retention
- Visual and editing choices

## Example Breakdown

Video Type:
Short-form lifestyle content

Observations:
- Strong opening visual draws attention immediately
- Cuts are timed to maintain engagement
- Minimal dead space between transitions

## Approach

- Analyze what keeps viewers watching
- Identify patterns in high-performing content
- Apply insights to editing and content creation
